# Foreign package managers — npm is the only canonical lockfile for
# this repo. A stray pnpm-lock.yaml makes Vercel auto-detect pnpm,
# which pulls a different dependency tree than the npm overrides in
# package.json are designed to enforce. The Error streak on
# 2026-07-15 through 2026-07-21 was caused by pnpm-lock.yaml +
# .pnpm-store/ landing in the working tree: prettier --check . then
# scanned 310 pnpm-store JSON files and exited 1, failing the proof.
# Defense in depth: keep these out of git AND out of the Vercel
# upload AND out of the prettier scan.
pnpm-lock.yaml
yarn.lock
bun.lockb
bun.lock
.pnpm-store/
.pnpm-debug.log*

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
